Circuit Breaker Design Pattern

Popular design pattern in microservices, it comes under Sustainable design pattern category
refer
https://medium.com/nerd-for-tech/design-patterns-for-microservices-circuit-breaker-pattern-ba402a45aac2

We can use circuit breaker design pattern to improve fault tolerance and resilience of microservices architecture and also to prevent
cascading of failure to other microservices.
